ol.li:
In the Rendering pane, select print from the
                        Emulate CSS media. This will activate the CSS selectors enclosed in
                        @media print {..}.

ul.li:
To figure out how the elements are mapped into PDF you can use this fragment in the customization
                    CSS:* {
   border: 1pt solid blue !important;
}

*:before(1000) {
   content:  oxy_name() !important;
   color: orange;
}

*:before(999) {
   content: "[ class= '" attr(class) "'] " !important;
   color: orange;
}This
                    will show the element name, its class attribute and will paint a blue border around each of the
                    elments in the output. It will not show the page margin boxes or some content elements that were
                    hidden.
